msgstr ":doc:`../setup/hardware`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:51
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/device_troubleshooting.rst:212
