msgstr "Показати список пристроїв IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:190
msgid ""
"In the printer configuration form, go to the :guilabel:`Printer Reports` tab "
"to configure the types of documents the printer automatically prints. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to open the :guilabel:`Add: Reports` pop-up "
"window. In the :guilabel:`Search...` bar, type `Shipping`, and "
"select :guilabel:`Shipping Labels`."
msgstr ""
"У формі конфігурації принтера перейдіть на вкладку :guilabel:`Звіти "
"принтера`, щоб налаштувати типи документів, які принтер друкує автоматично. "
"Натисніть :guilabel:`Додати рядок`, щоб відкрити спливаюче "
"вікно :guilabel:`Додати: Звіти`. У рядку :guilabel:`Пошук...` введіть "
"`Shipping` і виберіть :guilabel:`Shipping Labels`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:196
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Shipping Documents` report is for :ref:`export documents "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/export-doc>`."
msgstr ""
"Звіт :guilabel:`Shipping Documents` призначений для :ref:`експортних "
"документів <inventory/shipping_receiving/export-doc>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:None
msgid "Show carrier label report added to the *Printer Reports*."
msgstr "Звіт етикетки перевізника додано до *Звітів принтера*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:203
msgid ""
"After adding the :guilabel:`Shipping Labels` report in "
"the :guilabel:`Printer Reports` tab, ensure the :guilabel:`Report Type` "
"matches the IoT-connected printer's type."
msgstr ""
"Після додавання звіту :guilabel:`Етикетки доставки` на "
"вкладці :guilabel:`Звіти принтера` переконайтеся, що :guilabel:`Тип звіту` "
"відповідає типу принтера, підключеного до IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:206
msgid "For laser printers, set the :guilabel:`Report Type` to :guilabel:`PDF`."
msgstr ""
"Для лазерних принтерів встановіть :guilabel:`Тип звіту` на :guilabel:`PDF`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:207
msgid ""
"For Zebra printers, set the :guilabel:`Report Type` to :guilabel:`Text`."
msgstr ""
"Для принтерів Zebra встановіть :guilabel:`Тип звіту` на :guilabel:`Text`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:212
msgid "Shipping carrier label type"
msgstr "Тип етикетки перевізника доставки"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:214
msgid ""
"Next, complete the setup for the :doc:`third-party shipping connector <../"
"setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>`. After that, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Shipping Methods`, "
